The Glenn Beck Radio Show JUN-27-2013 THURS









The Glenn Beck Program

          
      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 06/27/2013



Thursday, June 27, 2013 1:01 PM



The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET



Glenn and the guys talk about the Supreme Court decision regarding same sex marriage.

 Also touches on the Trayvon Martin case and Senator Paul Ryan
 trying to sell immigration reform to the GOP in house.

 Laurie Dhue joins the show to discuss tonight's "For The Record" episode tonight on Blaze TV.
